Subject: Sincere Invitation | Salad Team Year-End Dinner & Appreciation Gathering

Dear Salad Team Colleagues,

Hello everyone!

As the year ends, I would like to extend my sincere gratitude to each of you for your hard work and dedication throughout the past year.

To express my appreciation and to enjoy a relaxed time together, I have arranged a year-end dinner and warmly invite you all to join.

【Event Details】

· Date & Time: [e.g., Wednesday, December 25, at 6:30 PM]
· Venue: [Restaurant Name & Address]
· Activities: Dinner and casual conversation

Please plan your schedule in advance. I look forward to having everyone join us. If you are unable to attend, kindly let me know ahead of time.

Let’s gather to celebrate a year of hard work and look forward to the journey ahead. I hope everyone continues to find both growth and joy in our work together.

If you have any questions, please feel free to reach out to me.

Thank you once again, and I look forward to a wonderful evening with all of you.

Best regards,

